title: Auto industry may be tough stretch for Apple Google other tech companies
text:
Auto industry may be tough stretch for Apple, Google, other tech companies 
TribLive Saturday 24th October, 2015 
FILE - In this May 13, 2014, file photo, a row of Google self-driving cars stands outside the Computer History Museum in Mountain View, Calif. Google has spent six years working on cars that can drive without human assistance. But the company says it doesn?t want the responsibility of building the robotic vehicles. (AP Photo/Eric Risberg, File)...
